            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3f5b60f06bb61d8c-687b9a twpub-3f5b60f06bb61d8c-9e9b4c twpub-3f5b60f06bb61d8c-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"chapter\"><p class=\"letter\">My dear Robinson,<br>\n<br>\n    It was to your account of a West-Country legend that this tale owes its inception. For this and for your help in the details all thanks.</p></div></div>"
        },
