            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-3f5b60f06bb61d8c-687b9a twpub-3f5b60f06bb61d8c-9e9b4c twpub-3f5b60f06bb61d8c-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"c15\"><div class=\"c2\">Please check the Project Gutenberg web pages for current donation methods and addresses. Donations are accepted in a number of other ways including checks, online payments and credit card donations. To donate, please visit: www.gutenberg.org/donate</div></div></div>"
